* bootstrap key should be in /var/lib/ceph/boostrap-osd/#{cluster}.keyring

* use whoami at mountpoint to discover osd id
* remove from crush, unmout etc in destroy method
* fsid is the uuid of the devmapper device
* individual osd definition in ceph.conf are not necessary anymore
* ceph.conf changes:

mon host = 1.1.1.1:6789, 1.1.1.2:6789, 1.1.1.3:6789

/var/lib/ceph/osd/ceph-#{osd_id}/fsid
/var/lib/ceph/osd/ceph-#{osd_id}/whoami


* upstart for monitors
touch /var/lib/ceph/mon/ceph-#{node.hostname}/done
touch /var/lib/ceph/mon/ceph[#{node.hostname}/upstart

service name ceph-mon-all-starter

* ceph disk activate (triggered by udev) will automatically setup upstart

service name "ceph-osd-all-starter"

service name "ceph-radosgw-all-starter"

* in osd configuration can set 'ceph osd crush location' = 'rack-alc1, row=m'
* in osd configuration can set 'osd crush initial weight' = 0
